Package org.bukkit.block.data.type

Interface Chest

All Superinterfaces:
BlockData, java.lang.Cloneable, Directional, Waterlogged
public interface Chest
extends Directional, Waterlogged
'type' represents which part of a double chest this block is, or if it is a single chest.
